Title: 窃窃 (Qieqie)/"Whisper"
Artist: 兰音Reine
description: lyric with original chinese (simplified) transcription and pinyin transliteration with accompanying approximate english translation.

该.. 如何去说不
gāi。。 rúhé qù shuō bu
How to say no

当你眼神与我眼神对视就已万劫不复
dāng nǐ yǎnshén yǔ wǒ yǎnshén duì shì jiù yǐ wànjiébùfù
When your eyes meet mine, it's already a point of no return.

对夜色太投入
duì yèsè tài tóurù
Too engrossed in the night

是我避之不及还是你心甘情愿没有退路
shì wǒ bì zhī bùjí háishì nǐ xīngānqíngyuàn méiyǒu tuìlù
Is it me trying to avoid it, or are you willingly without a way out?

呜 ~~ 
wū ~~
Oh ~~

窃窃的暧昧诱人中毒
qièqiè de àimèi yòu rén zhòngdú
Whispering ambiguity, a tempting poison

动魄惊心又销魂入骨
dòng pò jīng xīn yòu xiāohún rùgǔ
Startling and soul-consuming

欲望之下我宁可盲目
yùwàng zhī xià wǒ nìngkě mángmù
Under desire, I'd rather be blind

只要快乐什么都不在乎
zhǐyào kuàilè shénme dōu bùzàihū
As long as there's happiness, nothing else matters

窃窃的暧昧罪无可恕
qièqiè de àimèi zuì wú kě shù
Whispering ambiguity, unforgivable sin

情迷意乱却沉沦翻覆
qíng mí yì luàn què chénlún fānfù
Lost in emotion yet deeply entangled

不过几次心跳加速
bùguò jǐ cì xīntiào jiāsù
Just a few accelerated heartbeats

谁愿成为谁的掌中玩物
shéi yuàn chéngwéi shéi de zhǎngzhōng wánwù
Who wants to be a plaything in someone's hand?

该如何来驯服
gāi rúhé lái xùnfú
How to tame it

当我在你耳畔气息轻吐就已不由自主
dāng wǒ zài nǐ ěr pàn qìxí qīng tǔ jiù yǐ bùyóuzìzhǔ
When I whisper by your ear, you're already powerless

爱渴求着碰触
ài kěqiúzhe pèng chù
Love yearns for touch

只好把火掐灭承认对彼此温暖太贪图
zhǐhǎo bǎ huǒ qiā miè chéngrèn duì bǐcǐ wēnnuǎn tài tāntú
I can only extinguish the fire and admit to being too greedy for each other's warmth.

呜 ~~
wū ~~
Oh ~~

窃窃的暧昧诱人中毒
qièqiè de àimèi yòu rén zhòngdú
Whispering ambiguity, a tempting poison

身心堕落仍执迷不悟
shēnxīn duòluò réng zhímíbùwù
Body and soul fallen, yet still infatuated

甘甜至极我一再满足
gāntián zhìjí wǒ yīzài mǎnzú
Exquisitely sweet, I'm repeatedly satisfied

只要快乐什么都不在乎
zhǐyào kuàilè shénme dōu bùzàihū
As long as there's happiness, nothing else matters

窃窃的暧昧罪无可恕
qièqiè de àimèi zuì wú kě shù
Whispering ambiguity, unforgivable sin

谁都可以是裙下信徒
shéi dōu kěyǐ shì qún xià xìntú
Anyone can be a follower under the skirt

不过几次心神恍惚
bùguò jǐ cì xīnshén huǎnghū
Just a few moments of daze

为何你我偏要趋之若鹜
wèihé nǐ wǒ piān yào qūzhīruòwù
Why do you and I flock to it so eagerly?

